{"tid":1327354,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"窮絲買唔起防毒面具幫假j噴色 48蚊DIY左個萬用口罩","createTime":"2019-07-17T14:36:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-19T04:45:29.000Z","uid":39789,"like":21,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"ee62f99897028b8bbe68f1c7570011e05a9bf0b9","tid":1327354,"uid":39789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T14:36:06.000Z","msg":"話說最近好多絲打都學左男仔玩模型要噴色<br />\n聽講噴色<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">要好好保護自己</span><br />\n想買個好d嘅慮罐口罩但又買唔起<br />\n唯有諗下計<br />\n最慘貪平唔小心買左罐<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">英國製<span style=\"color: red;\">CS</span>牌</span>噴油<br />\n但全部英文睇唔明<br />\n睇到成份有咩<span style=\"color: red;\">5％</span><br />\n應該<span style=\"color: red;\">只防微粒嘅N95唔夠用</span><br />\n就買左個有活性炭防埋organic vapor嘅3M 8577<br />\n但8577<span style=\"color: red;\">只防95％微粒</span>都唔夠安全<br />\n要上都P100先防得晒所有<span style=\"color: red;\">微粒</span><br />\n所以再買多左塊3M 2091 P100濾棉<br />\n加埋先只係要48蚊<br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/z4JiWqT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fz4JiWqT.jpg&h=36971a08&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n然後塊棉唔知點解可以fit入個口罩到<br />\n不過就咁戴會比塊棉中間嘅膠環頂住唔舒服要用較剪將塊透明膠環剪走<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qw3KRYX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fqw3KRYX.png&h=ebc9a75d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n之後再戴就好fit喇<br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mzVk9L0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmzVk9L0.jpg&h=670cb504&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n平平地就整左個又防organic gas又防particles嘅口罩<br />\n星期日幫條假j上色應該都好安全<br />\n有冇巴絲都有玩開可以交流下實唔實用？"},{"pid":"076ea22bc29ea62ed9a8023194cb09631b078ee4","tid":1327354,"uid":40470,"like":38,"dislike":5,"score":33,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T14:41:31.000Z","msg":"其實智力低就唔好獻醜<br />\n<br />\n你剪左舊膠，你知唔知舊膠有乜用途？<br />\n<br />\n你學歷好低？<br />\n<br />\n弱智"},{"pid":"2b09c77c836153495a4e8df0a727803b05d289b7","tid":1327354,"uid":39789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ee62f99897028b8bbe68f1c75